"""
Persona-based context rewriting for collapse probability forecasting.

Rewrites scenario/history/data sections through each persona's professional lens.
Instructions are NEVER rewritten - only the factual context gets reframed.

Uses CognitiveProfile.to_natural_language() for persona descriptions.
Rewrites cached to disk (JSON) for reuse across experiments.
"""

